OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1781190689
OL,3,CFour jailed for 'brutal' killing of
OL,4,Cman, 24, who died from single stab
OL,5,Cwound
OL,7,FWatch: Footage from Devon and Cornwall
OL,8,FPolice of the events leading up to
OL,9,FDenva's murder.
OL,11,FFour men have been jailed for killing
OL,12,Fa 24-year-old man in Exmouth last year.
OL,14,FDenva Smith died after suffering a
OL,15,Fsingle stab wound to the left arm on
OL,16,FSaturday 31 May, 2025.
OL,18,FAfter a trial at Exeter Crown Court
OL,19,Fearlier this year, five defendants
OL,20,Fwere convicted for their roles in the
OL,21,Fkilling:
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
