CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1781190689
OL,3,CFour jailed for 'brutal' killing of
OL,4,Cman, 24, who died from single stab
OL,5,Cwound
OL,7,FAt a sentence hearing at Exeter Crown
OL,8,FCourt on Wednesday, 10 June, Ward and
OL,9,FMason were sentenced to life in prison
OL,10,Ffor the murder of the 24-year-old,
OL,11,Fwith a minimum of 23 years for Ward
OL,12,Fand 23 years and six months for Mason.
OL,14,FMason received a concurrent sentence
OL,15,Ffor the previous assault on another
OL,16,Fvictim.
OL,18,FDavis and Chadwick were jailed for 12
OL,19,Fyears for manslaughter, with Davies
OL,20,Fgiven an additional year for the phone
OL,21,Foffence.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
