PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1781190689
OL,3,CFour jailed for 'brutal' killing of
OL,4,Cman, 24, who died from single stab
OL,5,Cwound
OL,7,FHelliker will be sentenced at Exeter
OL,8,FCrown Court on 25 July.
OL,10,FThe Honourable Mr Justice Graham said
OL,11,FDenva's death had caused "utter
OL,12,Fmisery" for his family and that
OL,13,FDenva's mother found her son's passing
OL,14,F"impossible to process".
OL,16,FHe added that the murder was
OL,17,F"senseless".
OL,19,FWhat happened on the night Denva Smith
OL,20,Fdied?
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1781190689
OL,3,CFour jailed for 'brutal' killing of
OL,4,Cman, 24, who died from single stab
OL,5,Cwound
OL,7,FAt around 12:35am on 31 May last year,
OL,8,FDenva and an acquaintance were walking
OL,9,Fon Dinham Way when a group of five men
OL,10,Fapproached them.
OL,12,FThe group ran towards them causing
OL,13,FDenva to jump a crash barrier and run
OL,14,Fdown a slope into the area around the
OL,15,Fgarages at the end of Hawthorn Grove.
OL,17,FThe group allowed the man accompanying
OL,18,FDenva to escape and pursued Denva to
OL,19,Fthe bottom of the slope where he was
OL,20,Fstabbed by Ward.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1781190689
OL,3,CFour jailed for 'brutal' killing of
OL,4,Cman, 24, who died from single stab
OL,5,Cwound
OL,7,FDuring the attack, Denva lost a pair
OL,8,Fof sliders which were later located in
OL,9,Fa bin outside Ward's home address.
OL,10,FAlso recovered at the scene of the
OL,11,Fattack was a phone belonging to
OL,12,FHelliker.
OL,14,FAfter sustaining the fatal stab wound,
OL,15,FDenva was chased shoeless onto
OL,16,FHawthorn Grove and then onto Ashfield
OL,17,FClose. Three of the group continued to
OL,18,Fpursue him, with one shouting "get him
OL,19,Flad!".
OL,26,@zD@_OU{D@EO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
