OL,3,CFour jailed for 'brutal' killing of
OL,4,Cman, 24, who died from single stab
OL,5,Cwound
OL,7,FPolice were called just before 1am
OL,8,Ffollowing reports that a man had been
OL,9,Fstabbed.
OL,11,FDespite efforts from emergency
OL,12,Fservices, the 24-year-old died less
OL,13,Fthan an hour later.
OL,15,FWitnesses said they had heard banging
OL,16,Fand shouting and saw two men run from
OL,17,Fthe direction of Ashfield Close back
OL,18,Ftowards Hawthorn Grove.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1781190689
OL,3,CFour jailed for 'brutal' killing of
OL,4,Cman, 24, who died from single stab
OL,5,Cwound
OL,7,FDevon and Cornwall Police later
OL,8,Flearned that there was ill-feeling
OL,9,Fbetween Denva and Mason, and Denva and
OL,10,FWard who had previously been friends.
OL,12,FThe force's investigation found that
OL,13,Fsome of this animosity was closely
OL,14,Flinked to the supply of cocaine and
OL,15,Fcannabis in Exmouth.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1781190689
OL,3,CFour jailed for 'brutal' killing of
OL,4,Cman, 24, who died from single stab
OL,5,Cwound
OL,7,FDetective inspector Guy Biggar from
OL,8,Fthe major crime investigation team,
OL,9,Fsaid: "Denva Smith died in a
OL,10,Fstranger's garden after sustaining a
OL,11,Fsingle stab wound to the arm in May of
OL,12,Flast year.
OL,14,F"Prior to losing consciousness, Denva
OL,15,Fran for his life after being
OL,16,Fconfronted and attacked by the group
OL,17,Fcontaining the five defendants.
OL,26,@qD@GOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1781190689
OL,3,CFour jailed for 'brutal' killing of
OL,4,Cman, 24, who died from single stab
OL,5,Cwound
OL,7,F"By the jury's verdicts, Tom Ward and
OL,8,FBen Mason fully intended to cause
OL,9,FDenva at least serious harm when they
OL,10,Fattacked him that night, with Zac
OL,11,FDavies, Dylan Chadwick and Ben
OL,12,FHelliker all also present with the
OL,13,Fintent to cause him harm.
OL,15,F"No amount of ill-feeling between
OL,16,FDenva and those convicted can justify
OL,17,Fthe taking of a young life in such a
OL,18,Fviolent and brutal manner.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1781190689
OL,3,CFour jailed for 'brutal' killing of
OL,4,Cman, 24, who died from single stab
OL,5,Cwound
OL,7,F"Denva was a much-loved son, dad,
OL,8,Fbrother, grandson, uncle and nephew.
OL,9,FDuring the fatal attack he was
OL,10,Fisolated, alone and outnumbered.
OL,12,F"This was a dynamic and fast-paced
OL,13,Finvestigation which resulted in the
OL,14,Fdefendants being identified and
OL,15,Farrested.
OL,17,F"We welcome the sentences passed by
OL,18,Fthe judge and we hope that Denva's
OL,19,Ffamily and friends are able to feel
OL,20,Fsome form of closure as they attempt
OL,21,Fto move on with their lives."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU}D@]O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
